            {
              "speaker": "Chief Tess",
              "text": "What you want, skinny creature?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What is this place?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Chief Tess",
              "text": "Dis our home. It comfy, though we thinking of maybe getting more space up on land, above. But silly Corsair men live up there an' think dey own whole place."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Chief Tess",
              "text": "Maybe one day dat gonna change. Tess got plans."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Thanks."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I'll leave you alone, sorry."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
